{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Noun===
'''[[illegal]] [[combatant]]'''

# A captured fighter who engages in combat without meeting the requirements for a lawful belligerent according to the laws of war as specified in the [[w:Third Geneva Convention | Third Geneva Convention]].

====Synonyms====
*[[unlawful combatant]]
*[[unprivileged combatant]]

